{"tid":2493387,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美防長訪德 宣布增派五百名駐德美軍","createTime":"2021-04-18T00:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T15:41:15.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"57e2f039e256a8c008f522b3358728770a00c3bd","tid":2493387,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:29:52.000Z","msg":"美防長訪德 宣布增派五百名駐德美軍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%B2/20210413-%E7%BE%8E%E9%98%B2%E9%95%B7%E8%A8%AA%E5%BE%B7-%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%A2%9E%E6%B4%BE%E4%BA%94%E7%99%BE%E5%90%8D%E9%A7%90%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25B4%25B2%2F20210413-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%25BE%25B7-%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%25A2%259E%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%25A7%2590%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RInGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=93a91348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%B2/20210413-%E7%BE%8E%E9%98%B2%E9%95%B7%E8%A8%AA%E5%BE%B7-%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%A2%9E%E6%B4%BE%E4%BA%94%E7%99%BE%E5%90%8D%E9%A7%90%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國國防部長奧斯汀（Lloyd J. Austin）4月13日宣布，在與德國國防部長安內格雷特‧克朗普-卡倫鮑爾（Annegret Kramp-Karrenbauer）協商後，美國將在秋季前在德國增派500名軍人。<br />\n</strong><br />\n奧斯汀在德國國防部發表講話說：&ldquo;此次計畫增加美軍人員，凸顯了我們對德國和整個北約聯盟的承諾&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n此舉扭轉了美國上屆政府的政策，上屆政府希望大幅減少駐德美軍數量。拜登上任後，曾宣布了一項凍結從德國撤軍的政策。<br />\n<br />\n德國國防部長克朗普-卡倫鮑爾說：&ldquo;這是一個大好消息，（美國）不僅停止從德國撤軍，而且，恰恰相反，我們將能夠再迎來500名美軍&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">&ldquo;德國是我們最堅定的盟友之一，我們的關係建立在自由、民主、人權和法治的共同價值觀上。&rdquo;美國防長奧斯汀說，&ldquo;今天，這些原則正日益受到脅迫。在全球動態變化和充滿挑戰的安全環境中，德國將在未來繼續成為美國重要的安全和經濟夥伴。&rdquo;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n隨行官員表示，奧斯汀對德國的訪問表明拜登政府對兩國關係的重視。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;加強我們與德國的關係是拜登-賀錦麗政府的首要任務&rdquo;，奧斯汀說，&ldquo;強調我們對盟友和夥伴的堅定承諾是我的首要議程，這包括推進我們的跨大西洋夥伴關係，以及加強與北約盟友的合作。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n奧斯汀還說，這500名新增美軍將增強駐德美軍的現有能力，將在太空和網絡領域提供幫助，並在歐洲提供更多的電子戰能力，以及提高捍衛盟友的能力。<br />\n<br />\n德國是奧斯汀此行訪問的第一個歐洲國家。"},{"pid":"82bf058dd2f8159c231d1cfde5ef9f469393288b","tid":2493387,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab7e137a2a66b851bcc4fb96af9af2ff3316fa7","tid":2493387,"uid":151074,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T01:11:11.000Z","msg":"再奶共美軍就夾你隻肥婆走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bae7612261617dbcdb027887dcc2d53605ff1c","tid":2493387,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5fc95920cc315214fe0004b9c46c702d527241","tid":2493387,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d66f129e252d31aac61367ccbe3b393b1e4b56c","tid":2493387,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"打完仗七十幾年仲有戰勝國駐軍，元首知道呢件事實激醒再激死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d13220b69dedfb4257a84bedcf0c332f38ed88","tid":2493387,"uid":89857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d66f129e252d31aac61367ccbe3b393b1e4b56c","tid":2493387,"uid":331421,"like